  </span>
</p><p>
Altria Client Services
<br>Investor Relations
<br>(804) 484-8222
<br><br>Altria Client Services
<br>Media Affairs
<br>(804) 484-8897
</p><p>Source: Altria Group, Inc.</p></div>
